OL,3,CWoman's pension payments stopped for
OL,4,Cmonths after HMRC told her she was dead
OL,6,FAn 89-year-old from Cornwall's opened
OL,7,Fa letter from the government which
OL,8,Ftold her she was dead.
OL,10,FElizabeth Harris, who lives in
OL,11,FCarharrack near Redruth, received a
OL,12,Fletter from HMRC addressed to the
OL,13,Frepresentative for her estate on 15
OL,14,FJune June.
OL,16,FShe was shocked to read of her own
OL,17,Fdeath when she opened it.
