OL,3,CWoman's pension payments stopped for
OL,4,Cmonths after HMRC told her she was dead
OL,6,FDave said: "She completed a form for
OL,7,Fthe executor in which she said she was
OL,8,Fstill alive and put me down as the
OL,9,Fmain contact, and returned it on 22
OL,10,FJune. This is because she's hard of
OL,11,Fhearing so would struggle with all the
OL,12,Fphone calls.
OL,14,F"I phoned HMRC on 28 June and was told
OL,15,Fthey'd received the form, but for the
OL,16,Fpension to be reinstated I had to
OL,17,Fspeak to the Department for Work and
OL,18,FPensions."
OL,20,FDave was told the HRMC systems said
OL,21,FElizabeth had died on 11 May.
