OL,3,CWoman's pension payments stopped for
OL,4,Cmonths after HMRC told her she was dead
OL,6,FHe said: "I was told she's dead on one
OL,7,Fsystem, but alive on all the other
OL,8,Fsystems.
OL,10,F"I was told they could sort the
OL,11,Fproblem out but then a month later it
OL,12,Fstill wasn't in her bank account. I
OL,13,Fmade lots of calls and sent letters,
OL,14,Fbut by the end of July there was still
OL,15,Fnothing.
OL,17,F"This is when we really started to
OL,18,Fpanic."
OL,26,@nD@JOUrD@AOUyD@AOUzD@GO]
