OL,3,CWoman's pension payments stopped for
OL,4,Cmonths after HMRC told her she was dead
OL,6,FIt was not until Wednesday 7 August,
OL,7,Fafter Dave spoke to the press, that
OL,8,FElizabeth finally got the money she
OL,9,Fwas owed - with three months of
OL,10,Fpayments made.
OL,12,F"Within the last 24 hours due to media
OL,13,Fattention the payment has been made. I
OL,14,Fdid ask if she'd get any compensation,
OL,15,Fbut that was a no," he said.
OL,17,FAlthough this story has a happy
OL,18,Fending, there's a worry of other
OL,19,Fissues like this affecting other
OL,20,Fpeople.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
