OL,3,CWoman's pension payments stopped for
OL,4,Cmonths after HMRC told her she was dead
OL,6,F"Our main concern is how many people
OL,7,Fhas this affected? This can't be a one-
OL,8,Foff.
OL,10,F"I actually got a call from a former
OL,11,Ftax inspector thanking me for bringing
OL,12,Fthis problem to the attention of
OL,13,Fothers. Many elderly people might not
OL,14,Fhave people that could help them if
OL,15,Fthey were in this situation.
OL,17,F"It is ridiculous you need to go to
OL,18,Fthis length to get through the system,
OL,19,Fthere were so many hoops to jump
OL,20,Fthrough, it wasn't a simple process."
